What this does:

Loads Iris dataset directly (no need to download CSV manually).

Prints dataset structure, missing values, and summary statistics.

Groups data by species (target).

Creates 4 customized plots:

Line chart (Sepal length trend).

Bar chart (average sepal width per species).

Histogram (petal length distribution).

Scatter plot (sepal length vs petal length).

Prints insights at the end.

